Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Israeli forces opened machine-gun fire on 
Mazra'at al-Hamra' and nearby villages overnight. There were no 
reports of casualties. Flares were fired over Kafr Tibnit, 
Zawtar al- Sharqiyah, Zawtar al-Gharbiyah, and the al-Litani 
River basin. 
  Elsewhere, gunmen blew up cars belonging to Hasan Yasin and 
Muhammad Yasin in Khirbat Silm Town this morning. The Internal 
Security Forces immediately started investigating. The town of 
Khirbat Silm has been the scene of separate security incidents 
over recent weeks between the Amal Movement and Hizballah. 

